Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.30,0:00:16.12,OP,,0,0,0,,大厦的外墙 巨大的银幕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.15,0:00:26.75,OP,,0,0,0,,都会的女神 KISS KISS KISS 对我笑 SO SWEET I FOUND YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.55,0:00:33.60,OP,,0,0,0,,一亿个梦 会有十亿个机会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.62,0:00:41.42,OP,,0,0,0,,肯定对的路 NO NO NO没人会知道 DON'T CHEAT
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.33,0:00:50.72,OP,,0,0,0,,迷宫般的道路 只有我与你两人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.74,0:00:57.27,OP,,0,0,0,,CARRY ON CARRY ON 尝试走出一步的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.86,0:01:00.78,OP,,0,0,0,,CAN'T STOP IT NO WAY OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.85,0:01:03.66,OP,,0,0,0,,CAN'T STOP IT 永远地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.69,0:01:12.33,OP,,0,0,0,,CAN'T STOP IT 停不下来 HOW CAN YOU HOLD ME ON？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.24,0:01:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,终有一天、必定会…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,（刚才好险）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.59,0:01:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的，臭老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.54,0:01:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,发这种无聊的誓\N（唔？）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.84,0:01:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,（有什么意见）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.04,0:01:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,（就直接说出来）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.48,0:01:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那个切腹的约定，现在立即去给我取消
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.01,0:01:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你那乱七八糟的约定竟然把我也扯进去！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.63,0:02:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,（我拒绝）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.23,0:02:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,（男人和熊猫说一不二！）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.50,0:02:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道你会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.38,0:02:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我用妈妈的刀来送你一程
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.59,0:02:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,现在立即，在这切开你的肚皮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.15,0:02:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,（厉…厉害）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.99,0:02:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.22,0:02:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起，伯母
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.63,0:02:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,还要你帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.19,0:02:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这种小事没什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.91,0:02:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,别跑，别跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.16,0:02:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,乱子，危险！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.76,0:02:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,一淋热水，乱马变身体质就会被看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.31,0:02:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,万事休已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.05,0:03:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害，好厉害啊，乱子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.97,0:03:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,小霞，帮我拿明太子来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.37,0:03:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好，爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.44,0:03:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃  真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,对了，小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.42,0:03:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,听说你是乱马的未婚妻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.29,0:03:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.56,0:03:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这个我要了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.73,0:03:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,乱马他…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.03,0:03:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,来，爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.51,0:03:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,乱马他，像个男子汉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.74,0:03:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,以未婚妻的你来看认为怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.16,0:03:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那么，酷吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.76,0:03:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.43,0:03:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那么，帅吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.13,0:03:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.86,0:03:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才一直出现的奇怪停顿是什么意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.98,0:03:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,乱马的样子长得好像伯母你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.15,0:03:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.35,0:03:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,真的呢，坐在一起简直一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,转换一下话题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.07,0:04:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那么，乱马的兴趣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.27,0:04:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,兴趣好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是格斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是穿女装吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.72,0:04:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,女装？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这种没一点男子气概的兴趣？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,（是除草啦，太太）\N日文女装跟除草同音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.54,0:04:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,原来是那种除草啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.91,0:04:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了，刚刚我还真不知怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.76,0:04:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你啊，究竟跟我有什么仇恨啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.43,0:04:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我说了不好的事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.13,0:04:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,完完全全
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.40,0:04:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,乱马，你真的不想认回你妈妈吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.61,0:04:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,要我切腹还不如给小靡勒索比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.62,0:04:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,勒索？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.05,0:04:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.27,0:04:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这是身在福中不知福的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我和小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.67,0:04:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是想见妈妈，也已经见不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.23,0:05:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,乱马
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,什么，小靡？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.01,0:05:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,今次就不用你给我五千日元了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.16,0:05:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,亏我还一瞬间当真了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.98,0:05:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,乱子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.91,0:05:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,伯母，今晚要睡在这房间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,一起睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.66,0:05:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.37,0:05:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.63,0:05:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然说不能相认
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.37,0:05:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但你们是一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,最少一晚，好好相处一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.02,0:05:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那个，乱子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.19,0:05:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,小霞姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,早乙女伯母，说明天就要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.96,0:06:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,明天要回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.23,0:06:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,突然好像安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.46,0:06:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,乱马，乱马…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,原来是说梦话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,乱马
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.07,0:06:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,在梦中，也在找我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.32,0:06:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.49,0:06:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,乱马！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.37,0:06:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.37,0:06:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么没长得像个男子汉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好可怜的阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.42,0:06:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是做恶梦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是为了伯母，也是为了乱马
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.53,0:07:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,都不能就这样让他们分别
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.62,0:07:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那么，打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然遗憾没见到乱马和我丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,请下次再来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.44,0:07:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,再见伯母
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.71,0:07:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,再见，乱子也要保重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.32,0:07:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.39,0:07:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,再见，乱子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真好的热水啊，乱马
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.71,0:07:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,洗温泉啊，乐呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.29,0:07:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了，乱马？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.13,0:07:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.47,0:07:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈好像很寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.78,0:07:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,乱马
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.88,0:08:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,而你，竟像是赶走了瘟神般的开心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.22,0:08:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这臭老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这没办法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.03,0:08:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,如果没把你培养成男子汉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.33,0:08:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,父子俩都要一起切腹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.78,0:08:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这会痛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的，做这么无聊的约定切什么腹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,别再唠唠叨叨的了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起，我忘了东西没拿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.67,0:08:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，是伯母啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，乱子和熊猫先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,在玩水吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.06,0:08:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,请再来玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.43,0:08:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,再见伯母
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.78,0:08:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,伯母…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.35,0:08:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,伯母
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:08:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.50,0:09:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,伯母
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了，小茜？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.97,0:09:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我去见妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.25,0:09:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,现在还说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.09,0:09:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,可是已经约定了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.12,0:09:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这个星期日在公园
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.39,0:09:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,乱马，也想以男性的样子去见妈妈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.51,0:09:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我在你眼中究竟是怎样的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.69,0:09:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,乱马，真有男子汉气概
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,真是好酷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,真的长成了男人中的男人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.70,0:09:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,别让她知道我的变身体质就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,还有别太美化自己啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.25,0:09:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这件事，不能告诉叔叔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.22,0:09:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,（我听到了）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.33,0:09:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,（这样，到了星期天）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.33,0:09:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那么我…要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.30,0:09:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,乱马，等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.31,0:09:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:10:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然不是母亲节
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,给伯母的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.36,0:10:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢，小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,还磨磨蹭蹭干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.31,0:10:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么说呢，突然这样有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.79,0:10:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,她认得出我是她儿子吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.56,0:10:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋，竟担心这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,可以见到乱马？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.03,0:10:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,对，乱马的特征是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.75,0:10:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，等等，先别说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.08,0:10:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然很久没见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但毕竟是我儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,让我一眼就认出给你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.84,0:10:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.14,0:10:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,伯母她等你好久了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.15,0:10:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，乱马
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.16,0:10:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.29,0:10:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.81,0:11:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,从这里开始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.34,0:11:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我一步也不会让你过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么也要见妈妈的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.95,0:11:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,就先打倒我这爸爸再…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.71,0:11:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.65,0:11:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,等等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.12,0:11:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我是为了你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.39,0:11:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,为了你好才会…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.87,0:11:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,假如，乱马！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.01,0:11:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,明明要以男人姿态跟妈妈相认
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.85,0:11:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那时候却偏偏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.79,0:11:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,有人在泼水
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.96,0:11:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.36,0:11:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,就算小心避过了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.73,0:11:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,地下水管突然爆裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不会啦，那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,即使那也能避开了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.11,0:11:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,偶然路过的卖金鱼的人突然跌倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.66,0:11:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那种事不可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.00,0:12:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你不明白我是在避免你去切腹吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.88,0:12:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你这家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.27,0:12:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,（乱马不会来的，太太）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.87,0:12:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,（乱马不会来的，太太）\N（这就行了）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔\N（哇…！）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.64,0:12:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.38,0:12:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,乱马
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.81,0:12:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,（啊）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.18,0:12:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,乱马
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.03,0:12:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,终于到了吗，乱马
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,（糟了）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.03,0:12:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,长得真像你爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.83,0:12:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,伯母，不是啦不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.75,0:13:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜，你来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那个，乱马长得完全不像叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.35,0:13:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，先别说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.90,0:13:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然很久没见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.27,0:13:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但毕竟是我儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.17,0:13:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,今次我一定能一眼认出给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.99,0:13:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,乱马
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,（啊，乱马）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？在哪在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,乱马，这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.07,0:13:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,伯母，乱…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,被叔叔…带走了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.40,0:13:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.73,0:13:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,竟敢这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.20,0:13:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,等着我吧，妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.18,0:13:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定能找到你，跟你相认的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.05,0:13:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,还摆什么姿势啦，在那边在那边！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.95,0:13:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,（那边，那边）\N哪里，哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.66,0:13:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶，老爸那混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.31,0:14:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,伯母
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.29,0:14:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,乱马不来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.16,0:14:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,（怎么也好）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.11,0:14:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.51,0:14:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,在了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.11,0:14:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,（暴露身份的话就要切腹啊）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.86,0:14:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不暴露身份就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈，现在就让你看看我男子汉的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.53,0:14:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,乱马
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.79,0:14:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这…这是男孩子的手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,乱马
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.50,0:14:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.94,0:14:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,乱马，乱马…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.19,0:15:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,乱子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.47,0:15:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了，伯母？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.41,0:15:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起，我认错人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.48,0:15:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,（呼…）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.03,0:15:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,（太太真的那么想见乱马吗？）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,想见，现在就想立即见到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.33,0:15:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,（嘿嘿，那么…）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你想干什么，熊猫？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,（想要命的话就快走）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,（啊！）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.97,0:15:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,既然你要这样我也不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.37,0:15:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,伯母，到外边去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.45,0:15:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事，小茜？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.49,0:15:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,用这样下流的手段，混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.96,0:15:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.66,0:15:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,乱马，是不是不想见我？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.57,0:15:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.21,0:16:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,可是，等了这样久他还不出现
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.88,0:16:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,出是出现了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.88,0:16:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你这卑鄙家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.46,0:16:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,哼，有什么好嚣张的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.79,0:16:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你不也一样怕切腹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.73,0:16:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.13,0:16:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你有切开肚皮的觉悟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.45,0:16:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,总而言之
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.58,0:16:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想让妈妈看一下男子汉的我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.39,0:16:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸你就闭嘴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.20,0:16:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,还是说，想见我也不敢见吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.07,0:16:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,难道乱马…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.29,0:16:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,没有长成个男子汉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.64,0:16:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会，这不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.51,0:16:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了，乱子？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.09,0:17:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这种，只充一时的谎话\N迟早会被拆穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.27,0:17:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,反而只会让妈妈伤心而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.88,0:17:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,就是说你怕切腹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.51,0:17:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,（这才是我的儿子）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.58,0:17:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.45,0:17:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我…要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.83,0:17:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我肯定，乱马已长成为堂堂正正的男子汉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,伯母我相信着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.59,0:17:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.91,0:17:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,乱马
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.37,0:17:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.41,0:17:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我多管闲事，对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.31,0:17:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,因为伯母，是那么的想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.23,0:17:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,而我，却只想看看她高兴的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不过切腹也真是可怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.97,0:17:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不是在逼你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.08,0:18:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你这不是正在逼我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.49,0:18:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,乱马
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我好想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.04,0:18:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,（放水按钮，别坐）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.89,0:18:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,温泉喷出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是镭元素温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.98,0:18:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,乱马
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.18,0:18:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.89,0:18:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,乱…马？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:18:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,乱马
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.33,0:19:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.77,0:19:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,乱马
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.39,0:19:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,看到我真正的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.57,0:19:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈她…一定很失望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.37,0:19:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.88,0:19:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你很有男子气概啊，乱马
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.69,0:19:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,0:19:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,乱子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:19:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是乱子救我的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.39,0:20:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.16,0:20:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.82,0:20:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,原来那是梦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.46,0:20:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.80,0:20:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,乱马来救我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.71,0:20:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那样子真是太有男子汉气概了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.24,0:20:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,乱马
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我，见到乱马了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.46,0:20:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,伯母，那其实是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.40,0:20:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.07,0:20:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,够了，现在就让她当是梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.85,0:20:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那么，再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.18,0:20:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,终有一天，到我会变真正的男人为止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.19,0:20:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的梦，请你一定要记住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.03,0:20:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.90,0:20:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸，叔叔，茶放在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.61,0:20:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你，小霞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.01,0:20:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,经常麻烦你，真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,将军
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.62,0:20:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，卑鄙这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.65,0:20:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,早乙女兄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.42,0:20:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么总是这样逃避问题啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.66,0:20:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.26,0:20:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我其实
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.04,0:20:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我啊，我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.57,0:21:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,真是很喜欢你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.71,0:21:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,笨死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.84,0:21:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你这是什么眼光！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.81,0:21:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.75,0:21:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,慢走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.26,0:21:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,要迟到了，乱马
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.46,0:21:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道啦，烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.73,0:21:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.75,0:21:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你干什么，小茜？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.66,0:21:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.17,0:21:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.55,0:21:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.05,0:21:58.89,ED,,0,0,0,,留在我身边 近得可以四目相投
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.94,0:22:03.14,ED,,0,0,0,,可是温柔和笑脸却交错而过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.90,0:22:07.33,ED,,0,0,0,,你装作没发觉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.50,0:22:11.76,ED,,0,0,0,,又赶着去恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.78,0:22:20.22,ED,,0,0,0,,即使如此 在那闪烁的山丘上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.65,0:22:35.63,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1\fsp1\pos(280,389.333)}断断续续的故事 只是单纯的演戏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.65,0:22:35.63,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1\fsp1\pos(366.667,472)}包裹着两人的彩虹 能实现一个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.65,0:22:43.45,ED,,0,0,0,,有太阳的气味呢 无论是你的梦想 还是你的衬衫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.52,0:22:52.37,ED,,0,0,0,,充满希望的眼睛 能把一切都变辉煌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.01,0:23:00.97,ED,,0,0,0,,所以最重要的梦想 千万别放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.73,0:23:10.10,ED,,0,0,0,,只要一直保有飞向天空的力量和勇气
